<br>
It is definitely likely that more than one guild will get on sev rot per rotation over the next year+. A prudent guild with good timing could kill sev 2, 3, 4+ times more than any rot guild by simply waiting till someone enters the rot, and racing the guild up that the new rot guild inserted prior to.<br>
